getBodyResponse.code:
function getBodyResponse(body) {
	return {
		id: body.id,
		surveyId: body.survey_id,
		ipAddress: body.ip_address,
		totalTime: body.total_time,
		collectorId: body.collector_id,
		recepientId: body.recepient_id,
		responseStatus: body.response_status,
		customVariables: body.custom_variables,
		dateCreated: new Date(body.date_created),
		dateModified: new Date(body.date_modified),
		metadata: body.metadata
  }
}
